-- Activist Pershing Square starts process to change Allergan board
-- 
-- Mon Jun 02, 2014 08:48AM EDT
-- None



June 2 (Reuters) - Activist investor Pershing Square on Monday said it launched a process to call a special meeting of Allergan Inc <AGN.N> shareholders, a move that could turn over most of the drug company's board and open the door to a takeover by Valeant Pharmaceuticals Inc <VRX.TO>.

